  "title": "Production Control Executive (Electronics Mfg/ Loyang Area)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Plan and prepare section schedule, daily production performance and stock report.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with respective sections to ensure on-time delivery.</li>\n  <li>Daily monitoring of WIP and Finished goods against sales order balance.</li>\n  <li>Monitoring on the shop floor and attend daily production meeting to ensure they follow according to schedule.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Business Management /Manufacturing Engineering or its equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Good communication, interpersonal and presentation skills.</li>\n  <li>Independent, creative, resourceful and able to take pressure.</li>\n  <li>Computer literate.</li>\n  <li>Experience in Production planning &amp; Electronics manufacturing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>5 days work week</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Electronics Engineering</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Loyang Area</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested Applicants, kindly email your detailed resume to <strong>hr@tempserv.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Tempserv Pte Ltd</strong></p>\n<p>License No: 06C3745</p>\n<p><strong>Attention: Audris Teo / EA Personnel No: R1102063</strong></p>",
